metadata.name: Pray For Peace
metadata.description:
In the middle of madness and horror people are looking for different ways to save themselves. 
Lilu (one of the Femmes Bizarre fam www.femmesbizarre.com) has found some peace near her place of power â€” the sacred Western Wall.
And we keep believing in humanity and help. 
All proceeds will be donated to The Voices of Children Foundation. Guys help Ukrainian kids affected by the war.
